modShortDescription: This mod adds nails to most wooden blocks and items that should have nails in their recipes. It adds bent nails into the world.
modDescription:
This mod adds nails to most wooden blocks and items that should have nails in their recipes. It adds bent nails into the world.

When destroying blocks use a hammer to get straight nails or you get bent nails. Repairing blocks requires nails. More nails and bent nails added to loot spawns.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/doughphunghus/7D2D-Doughs-Khelldons-Mods-a19/tree/main/Khelldon-GetNailed)** for A19
